Potential Benefits
You may or may not receive direct medical benefit from participation in this research study.
The study is designed to evaluate treatment effects in a controlled setting and no guarantee
of clinical improvement can be made. Your participation contributes to scientific understanding
that may benefit future patients with similar conditions.

Alternatives
Alternative treatment options are available outside this trial and can include standard-of-care
therapies, supportive care, or no treatment. You should discuss alternatives with your physician
before deciding whether to enroll.

