Regulatory and Safety Statement
This study is conducted according to ICH E6(R3) Good Clinical Practice principles and all
applicable national regulations. Adverse events are reviewed by qualified investigators and
reported in accordance with sponsor safety procedures. Data quality checks, source verification,
and monitoring visits may be performed by authorized personnel. Participation remains voluntary
throughout the trial duration.

Participant Acknowledgment
